import React from 'react';
import { Card, CardContent, Typography, Grid } from '@mui/material';
import { motion } from 'framer-motion';
import TempIcon from '@mui/icons-material/AcUnit'; // Example icon
import HumidityIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Opacity'; // Example icon
import WindSpeedIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Air'; // Example icon

function Homepage({ predictions }) {
    return (
        <motion.div
            initial={{ opacity: 0 }}
            animate={{ opacity: 1 }}
            transition={{ duration: 0.5 }}
        >
            <Grid container spacing={3}>
                {/* Weather Prediction Section */}
                <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
                    <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom style={{ fontWeight: "bold", color: "#BBDEFB" }}>
                        Weather Prediction
                    </Typography>
                    <Grid container spacing={3}>
                        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
                            <Card style={{
                                backgroundColor: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2)",
                                borderRadius: "10px",
                                boxShadow: "0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)",
                                textAlign: 'center',
                                padding: "20px",
                                height: "180px" // Increased height
                            }}>
                                <CardContent>
                                    <TempIcon style={{ fontSize: 40, color: '#BBDEFB' }} />
                                    <Typography variant="h6" style={{ color: '#BBDEFB' }}>Avg Temp</Typography>
                                    <Typography variant="h5" style={{ color: 'white' }}>{predictions[0]?.avg_temp || 'N/A'}Â°C</Typography>
                                    <Typography variant="body2" style={{ color: 'white', marginTop: "8px" }}>
                                        Average temperature for today.
                                    </Typography>
                                </CardContent>
                            </Card>
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
                            <Card style={{
                                backgroundColor: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2)",
                                borderRadius: "10px",
                                boxShadow: "0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)",
                                textAlign: 'center',
                                padding: "20px",
                                height: "180px" // Increased height
                            }}>
                                <CardContent>
                                    <HumidityIcon style={{ fontSize: 40, color: '#BBDEFB' }} />
                                    <Typography variant="h6" style={{ color: '#BBDEFB' }}>Humidity</Typography>
                                    <Typography variant="h5" style={{ color: 'white' }}>{predictions[0]?.humidity_9am || 'N/A'}%</Typography>
                                    <Typography variant="body2" style={{ color: 'white', marginTop: "8px" }}>
                                        Humidity level measured this morning.
                                    </Typography>
                                </CardContent>
                            </Card>
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
                            <Card style={{
                                backgroundColor: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2)",
                                borderRadius: "10px",
                                boxShadow: "0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)",
                                textAlign: 'center',
                                padding: "20px",
                                height: "180px" // Increased height
                            }}>
                                <CardContent>
                                    <WindSpeedIcon style={{ fontSize: 40, color: '#BBDEFB' }} />
                                    <Typography variant="h6" style={{ color: '#BBDEFB' }}>Wind Speed</Typography>
                                    <Typography variant="h5" style={{ color: 'white' }}>{predictions[0]?.wind_speed_9am || 'N/A'} km/h</Typography>
                                    <Typography variant="body2" style={{ color: 'white', marginTop: "8px" }}>
                                        Wind speed recorded this morning.
                                    </Typography>
                                </CardContent>
                            </Card>
                        </Grid>
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
                {/* Other Sections... */}
            </Grid>
        </motion.div>
    );
}

export default Homepage;
